Fault Injection Toolkit
author: raymond medeiros (grandmasterlogic@gmail.com)

[requirements]

In order to use the FIT Writer you must install Ruby Pcap:

cd src/third_party/pcap
ruby extconf.rb
make
make install

Mac OS X (PPC) Users should preform these additional steps prior to installing Ruby Pcap:

mv extconf_ppc.rb extconf.rb
mv mkmf_ppc.rb mkmf.rb

[documentation]

* http://fit.berlios.de

